{"tid":1638253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多行動進行中，但有一件事大家日日都可以做","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:12:11.000Z","uid":36797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82e54ee5d2c2ce7cc8fa00f2e7fc2c625ef2c5e3","tid":1638253,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"改下你地啲用字！<br />\n人地用曱甴兩隻字，就磨滅哂成班黑警既良心，因為日日聽會潛移默化。<br />\n唔知你地有無留意，好多記者都改左口唔叫手足做示威者，叫佢地做黑衫市民。<br />\n所以我地每日同人傾計，喺巴士餐廳講野，上網開post，都一定要改用字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好叫阿sir madam，叫差佬差婆，甚或叫黑警；<br />\n唔好叫警嫂，叫警妻，甚或叫狗乸；<br />\n唔好講「今日搞邊區」，應該係「今日邊區有活動」；<br />\n唔好叫藍絲商店，佢地係賣港商店；<br />\n如果有補充麻煩咁多位手足。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家同意用字既威力，可以睇下依個post，提高香港人排警精神。<br />\n<br />\n黑警不是香港人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591661</a>"},{"pid":"3fe453c6cffe83fd98d39250ac3f9d106b6d4358","tid":1638253,"uid":318903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6HC7uQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6HC7uQ.jpg&h=fec6c2ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d131fa2a3d5c428c248bb12a6f46b9f294bbb2a","tid":1638253,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"P牌推"},{"pid":"72ccf57a2012675124c46e590b884426c385b08c","tid":1638253,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}